{
  "stem": "10829.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He used to deal in-- in cattle, deal in land.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But mostly he would deal with the-- with the-- with the Polacks and the Ukraines in the villages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my dad and mom had a-- a-- a-- store, trading post, in one of the villages outside the city.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then when I was born, which was already the second child, we moved into-- to Trochenbrod, and we took one of the houses that my grandfather had owned, and that was our house that he turned it over.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Turned it over to us, and my dad bought it from-- from my zaide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And that's where we lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he knew, zaide knew all the Polacks and all the Ukraines, and used to deal with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had some good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had some that were his enemies, but he knew that whole area, and so did my dad.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you describe your household, that is your-- your immediate family and the other members of the household, before the war?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, to the best of my recollection, at that time, we had-- there were three of us kids, my brother, which is the youngest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's three years younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister was a year older than I am.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And myself.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And mom and dad used to be in the house, and we had my grandmother, Tsuppie.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She used to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's my dad's mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In those days, she looked like an old lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- considering the age, you got to-- you've got to think about-- We-- they're saying now, in retrospect, everybody thinks that we were rich in Poland.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, you talk to almost any immigrant, and they say they were rich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had bread and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were rich.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
